<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>No Reply Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello <%= name %></h1>
    <p>You have received a reply to your question in the course "<%= title %>".</p>
    <p><strong>Question:</strong> <%= question %></p>
    <p><strong>Reply:</strong> <%= reply %></p>
    <p>Best regards,<br/>SmartLearn Team</p>
    <p>Thank you for using our platform!</p>
</body>
</html>